# Tanden Open Handbook

Open handbook site for Tanden Inc. — publishing company culture, policies, and ways of working.

## Stack

Next.js 16 (App Router) + Fumadocs + React 19 + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS v4 (no tailwind.config) + Biome (no ESLint/Prettier) + bun. Deployed on Vercel.

## Structure

- `content/docs/` — MDX source files (philosophy, principles, systems, lifecycle, tools)
- `app/docs/[[...slug]]/` — Doc pages via Fumadocs
- `app/(home)/` — Landing page
- `app/llms.txt/`, `llms-full.txt/`, `llms.mdx/` — LLM-readable endpoints
- `app/og/docs/` — OG image generation
- `components/ai/` — LLMCopyButton, ViewOptions
- `lib/source.ts` — Fumadocs source loader (`source.getPage()`, `source.getPageTree()`)
- `lib/layout.shared.tsx` — Git config (`tanden-inc/tanden-docs`) and shared layout options
- `source.config.ts` — Fumadocs MDX config, content dir: `content/docs`

## Commands

- `bun run dev` / `bun run build` / `bun run lint` / `bun run format`
- `bun run types:check` — fumadocs-mdx → next typegen → tsc
